35:36.343 --> 35:38.220
but I want nothing to do with this.

35:39.555 --> 35:40.973
Are we good?

35:42.475 --> 35:44.185
Are we good?

35:44.977 --> 35:46.895
Yeah, we're good.

35:48.730 --> 35:50.315
Tell everyone I wasn't up for it,

35:50.398 --> 35:52.277
and I'll see you
back at the station tomorrow.

36:06.707 --> 36:08.208
Put your hands up, pal.

36:09.502 --> 36:11.212
Stand up slow. You know the drill.

36:14.423 --> 36:16.383
- Drop it.
- Uh-uh.

36:16.467 --> 36:17.385
Put it down.

36:17.468 --> 36:19.220
Why would you do that?

36:19.303 --> 36:20.555
I said put it down.

36:20.638 --> 36:22.557
I was listening to you and your partner,

36:23.598 --> 36:24.850
and it got me wondering.

36:24.933 --> 36:28.395
When did guys like us
lose that youthful idealism?

36:28.478 --> 36:29.897
Drop it now.

36:29.980 --> 36:31.690
I understand, man, this is hard,

36:31.773 --> 36:33.192
letting something like that

36:33.275 --> 36:35.068
slip through your dirty fingers, ain't it?

36:35.152 --> 36:37.153
But I'm doing you a favour.

36:37.238 --> 36:39.365
That money, it's not mine.

36:39.448 --> 36:40.825
We know it's not yours.

36:40.908 --> 36:42.535
But the people it belongs to,

36:42.618 --> 36:44.995
trust me,
you and I do not wanna screw with.

36:46.330 --> 36:47.873
Thanks for the tip.

36:47.957 --> 36:50.585
I'm always looking for detectives
with your perspective.

36:51.418 --> 36:53.253
Leave it, walk away,

36:53.337 --> 36:55.297
and I will make you
so much more, I promise.

36:55.380 --> 36:57.425
- Put down the goddamn gun!
- Can't do it.

36:57.508 --> 37:00.052
- Do it. I'll blow your head off!
- No, you won't do that.

37:00.135 --> 37:01.470
I'm gonna count to three.

37:01.553 --> 37:04.390
One, two...

37:08.893 --> 37:10.145
Hey, hey.

37:10.228 --> 37:11.563
I couldn't let him do that.

37:11.647 --> 37:12.690
I know, I know.

37:12.773 --> 37:14.233
- Come on, come on.
- Oh no.

37:14.317 --> 37:15.652
It's gonna be alright.

37:15.735 --> 37:17.778
Is he OK?

37:19.238 --> 37:20.823
He's gonna be OK, right?

37:23.200 --> 37:25.787
- We'll get him some help!
- He's dead.

37:25.870 --> 37:27.078
No, he's not.

37:27.162 --> 37:28.747
- Yeah, he is.
- No, he's not.

37:28.830 --> 37:30.457
He was gonna shoot you, right?

37:32.125 --> 37:34.628
He was gonna shoot you, yeah?

37:35.378 --> 37:36.797
Oh, my God!

37:37.465 --> 37:40.050
I didn't mean to do that! Oh, my God!

37:40.133 --> 37:41.635
It's OK! It's OK! It's OK!

37:41.718 --> 37:43.220
- I didn't mean to do that!
- It's OK!

37:43.303 --> 37:44.805
- I didn't mean to do that!
- Breathe!

37:44.888 --> 37:47.140
It's OK, it's OK! It was an accident.

37:47.223 --> 37:49.518
Come on, now. Come on, now.
Get it together!

37:49.602 --> 37:50.812
- It was an accident!
- OK.

37:53.313 --> 37:55.858
Reggie, look at that. Cops are gone.

37:55.942 --> 37:59.028
Look, cops are gone, OK?
This boat's leaving soon.

37:59.112 --> 38:01.113
Come on, we're a team. We gotta do this.

38:01.197 --> 38:02.948
We gotta clean this mess up.

38:03.032 --> 38:04.533
I was trying to help you.

38:04.617 --> 38:06.743
- It's an accident.
- We're gonna clean this up.

38:06.827 --> 38:09.538
Then we're gonna get the hell out of here.
OK? We gotta do that now.

38:09.622 --> 38:11.207
What are we gonna do with him?

38:12.082 --> 38:14.085
What are we gonna do with him?

38:14.960 --> 38:16.545
He's going to Mexico.

38:41.362 --> 38:43.613
Wes! Check it out!

38:45.282 --> 38:48.368
I thought you might
wanna play with your friends or with me.

38:48.452 --> 38:50.747
What do you say? Little one-on-one?

38:50.830 --> 38:53.665
I have some free time,
and ten bucks says you can't beat me.

38:53.748 --> 38:55.208
No, thanks.

39:38.835 --> 39:40.670
What the hell are you doing here?

39:40.755 --> 39:43.215
If you'd just answer my calls,
we wouldn't need to be here.

39:43.298 --> 39:45.550
No, we're done. I told him everything.

39:45.633 --> 39:47.845
I told Nats everything, you hear me?

39:47.928 --> 39:49.555
I don't owe you anything anymore.

39:49.638 --> 39:52.348
- Look, I'm worried about you.
- You got nothing on me now.

39:52.433 --> 39:54.058
- You don't get it.
- I don't get what?

39:54.143 --> 39:55.978
They're gonna kill you.

39:56.062 --> 39:58.313
Oh, now you're worried about me?

39:58.397 --> 40:00.273
You know what?

40:00.983 --> 40:02.108
Shove it up your ass!

40:02.192 --> 40:03.735
- Val...
- I'm done!

40:03.818 --> 40:05.863
Don't you ever call me again!

40:05.947 --> 40:07.448
You are not... Val!

40:29.178 --> 40:31.138
What about her in the red dress?

40:33.348 --> 40:35.267
She looks like an escort.

40:35.350 --> 40:37.268
That's never stopped you before.

40:39.938 --> 40:41.357
Her?

40:41.440 --> 40:42.733
Not bad,

40:42.817 --> 40:45.152
but look at that tacky dress. Please.

40:45.235 --> 40:48.447
You're really being difficult tonight,
hmm?

40:48.530 --> 40:50.950
Stop thinking about everyone back home.

40:51.033 --> 40:52.702
It will work out.

40:52.785 --> 40:54.412
Papa gave this to us

40:54.495 --> 40:56.455
because he knew that we could handle it,

40:56.538 --> 40:57.748
and we can.

40:57.832 --> 40:59.667
We'll give Luca a month.

40:59.750 --> 41:02.920
As long as he does what we say,
it will work out.

41:03.003 --> 41:04.797
What do you see in him?

41:05.840 --> 41:07.508
Authenticity.

41:23.023 --> 41:25.358
He looks, um, innocent.

41:25.442 --> 41:27.027
Could be fun!

41:27.110 --> 41:29.028
But it's your turn tonight.

41:29.112 --> 41:30.948
Am I counting?

41:56.807 --> 41:58.683
I want to give you to my brother.

42:36.513 --> 42:38.098
It's not your fault.

42:39.725 --> 42:41.060
Reggie, it's not your fault.

42:43.062 --> 42:44.730
I wanna go home.

42:44.813 --> 42:46.148
Alright.

42:57.367 --> 42:59.118
I saw a lot of police.

42:59.202 --> 43:01.913
Payment's in full. It's on its way.

43:01.997 --> 43:04.040
But there was a little problem.

43:04.123 --> 43:06.668
Get some extra cargo, dead cop.

43:06.752 --> 43:09.003
So you make your problem our problem?

43:09.087 --> 43:10.130
I had to be flexible,

43:10.213 --> 43:11.673
so now you do too.

43:11.757 --> 43:13.508
That's how we get things done.

43:15.760 --> 43:18.680
Actually, Declan,
our deal with you is over.

43:19.682 --> 43:21.933
You're in the middle of a war here,

43:22.017 --> 43:24.102
and that is not good for business.

43:46.292 --> 43:47.877
Who is that guy?

43:54.257 --> 43:56.177
Maybe you should walk away.

43:57.720 --> 44:00.930
Just... Just leave it all.

44:04.308 --> 44:06.395
We could go anywhere, right?

44:08.813 --> 44:10.398
Declan?

44:12.525 --> 44:14.235
What are you thinking?

44:15.570 --> 44:17.572
This would be the right time.

44:18.990 --> 44:20.533
Leave it all.

44:22.703 --> 44:24.287
Just leave it all.

44:28.667 --> 44:31.920
<i>Next time on </i> Bad Blood:
- Eight fentanyl overdoses at the weekend.

44:32.003 --> 44:33.843
<i>A couple of kids
they found on a reserve.</i>

44:33.922 --> 44:35.298
We're shutting it down.

44:35.382 --> 44:37.550
Pop's says we're out, OK,
but I'm still in.

44:37.633 --> 44:39.887
Dealers are mixing fentanyl with cocaine.

44:39.970 --> 44:41.597
Who would put poison in drugs?

44:41.680 --> 44:43.598
Teresa and Christian are who you want.

44:43.682 --> 44:46.060
Well, we want you to only buy from us.
No more Declan.

44:46.143 --> 44:49.688
Right now, a gangster is running
a better investigation than we are.

44:49.772 --> 44:51.065
Tell me everything.

44:51.148 --> 44:52.858
- Hi, Enzo.
- I don't know you.

44:52.942 --> 44:54.818
Nellie Bullock, RCMP.

44:54.902 --> 44:57.278
<i>The only way we win is to get them...</i>

44:57.362 --> 45:00.073
to rip themselves apart from the inside.

